{"tid":1667744,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友呀媽第一次遊行","createTime":"2019-10-21T15:34:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T15:41:50.000Z","uid":243080,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"934d3ee6670f105843f508ba98fc42c18169b2ed","tid":1667744,"uid":243080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:34:56.000Z","msg":"雖然佢明時都係黃，但身體唔好冇出過去，只係拖過一次手，星期日佢終於第一次出去啦！好感動，因為就算喺屋企幾嬲都好，都唔夠行出嚟實在！<br />\n<br />\n大家一定要叫身邊嘅人坐言起行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出咗嚟會更加明白，最多早出早走保護佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n後記：行完佢兩母子喺茶記講得勁大聲，我好尷尬，仲以為佢地嬲得濟大聲咗唔知，原土來係特登畀啲藍絲聽，效果非常好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6375674a9f30118acb8466d3b5bf91253ced2b27","tid":1667744,"uid":244723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:35:33.000Z","msg":"其實好多黃都唔敢出去行 <br />\n會覺得遊行好恐怖"},{"pid":"b0e918f0a76a737ec4d8118f2c13d211cc4f5c0c","tid":1667744,"uid":136893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:35:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">入黎認人啊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n義士唔係condom，入黎認人啊！（1021被捕人士整合po）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1667412\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1667412</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5453c07e7e35441825960bc81c4729ac54214f90","tid":1667744,"uid":114252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:38:46.000Z","msg":"你男朋友有你依個女友真係好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n價值觀一樣仲會照顧埋佢屋企人<br />\n三生有幸啦！"},{"pid":"a93eaf7eace6624165f5b307f8112428b0b7b724","tid":1667744,"uid":114252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:41:50.000Z",